'''Fardhexo'''  ({{lang-ar|الوسطى}}; {{lang-en|middle finger}}) waa [[far]]ta [[sadex]]aad ee [[gacan]]ta [[dad]]ka. Fartani waxay u dhexaysaa [[Murdiso (Murugsato)|murdisada]] (murugsato) iyo farta faadumo [[Faraanti galis (faadumo)|(faraanti galis]]), sida badan waa farta ugu dheer faraha.

Fartaan iyo [[suul]]ka markii la isku cadaadiyo ka dibna la sii daayo waxaa ka dhasha dhawaq dheer, oo loo adeegsado soo jeedin ama baraarujinta cid loo dan leeyahay taasi oo loo yaqaano '''Suuldhabaale''' (en: snapping).<ref>[[:en:Finger_snapping|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Finger_snapping]]</ref>

